sub_title: Project Manager at the European Football for Development Network
summary:
Project Manager at EFDN. Coordinating European-level projects to support the inclusion of disadvantaged groups, changing their lives through football. Current projects:
- Special Champions League (participants with intellectual disability)
- Welcome through Football (inclusion of refugees)
- Exchanges (both staff and youth)
- EFDN Conference (biannual, hosting 200+ delegates from CSR in football)

‚öΩ Football player and coach
